headline: Eaton to announce fourth quarter 2025 earnings on February 3, 2026
summary: DUBLIN, January 20, 2026--Intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) will announce fourth quarter 2025 earnings on Tuesday, February 3, 2026, before the opening of the New York Stock Exchange. The company will host a conference call at 11 a.m. Eastern time that day to discuss fourth quarter 2025 earnings results.
